      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape\u2014super reliable and perfect for anyone looking for a dependable car that still looks great on the road. I've taken good care of it, so it's ready for its next adventure with you! It runs like a dream and is just waiting for a new home. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
