      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This unit delivers a visceral, naturally aspirated experience paired with a precise 6-speed manual transmission. Key enthusiast concerns have been addressed: the VANOS system is serviced, and the chassis remains rigid with a healthy rear subframe. Equipped with the M-Variable Differential Lock and a balanced 50/50 weight distribution, this car offers exceptional turn-in and corner-exit traction. A well-sorted example of BMW's finest engineering, optimized for performance.",
